    "description": "<strong>Turbo Shell</strong> is a fast-paced 2D platformer with a unique movement mechanic: instead of running and jumping, you push and pull yourself through a sci-fi world with the help of the EPS (Egg Propulsion System). <br><br>The free demo includes the first world with 16 levels.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Pick up the EPS and get going</strong></h2> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713420/extras/17b18e803a8ec918892e0574ef6a4eba.poster.avif?t=1753944127\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713420/extras/17b18e803a8ec918892e0574ef6a4eba.webm?t=1753944127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713420/extras/17b18e803a8ec918892e0574ef6a4eba.mp4?t=1753944127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The EPS (Egg Propulsion System) allows you to glide through the sci-fi world of Turbo Shell: push yourself off surfaces within a short range using the blue ray, or pull yourself towards others using the orange ray.<br><br>Using the EPS is easy to learn. By perfecting your moves, you'll find even faster and more efficient ways to complete a level. Enjoy the rewarding feeling of skillfully flying through the space station and climb up the ranks on the leaderboard.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Overcome obstacles and avoid hazards</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713420/extras/d2f0e540628333c88658eafcae4b65ae.poster.avif?t=1753944127\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713420/extras/d2f0e540628333c88658eafcae4b65ae.webm?t=1753944127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713420/extras/d2f0e540628333c88658eafcae4b65ae.mp4?t=1753944127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Sizzling laser barriers, flying buzzsaws and hazardous corridors will pave your path. Avoid them to make sure you won't splash! <br><br>Turbo Shell is a precision platformer and completing levels without getting smashed will become more difficult on the way. Instant respawns and checkpoints will help you stay motivated and reach your goal.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Collect all Targets</strong></h2> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713420/extras/25b276cbf0d6bdb7e15aa2bf4034880f.poster.avif?t=1753944127\" width=600 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713420/extras/25b276cbf0d6bdb7e15aa2bf4034880f.webm?t=1753944127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713420/extras/25b276cbf0d6bdb7e15aa2bf4034880f.mp4?t=1753944127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The universe as we know it is in danger - but as Craig, you can save it by collecting targets that are scattered throughout each level. Make sure to reach them all in high-speed to get rewarded with a spot on the leaderboard!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713420/extras/0b1d392013206b5cbccf910ddf209635.poster.avif?t=1753944127\" width=600 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713420/extras/0b1d392013206b5cbccf910ddf209635.webm?t=1753944127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Unique movement mechanic:</strong> <br>Push and pull yourself through space - in the first game that's both repulsive and attractive at the same time.<br></li><li> <strong>Fast-paced precision platformer: </strong> <br>Collect all targets as fast as you can - but beware of the deadly hazards...<br></li><li> <strong>Challenging and rewarding:</strong> <br>Prepare to splash. A lot. Instant respawns will get you going again in no time!</li></ul>",
